  "title": "Senior Facilities Maintenance Technician | Gross up to $5.5k | Shift Hours - ZH",
  "description": "<p>Salary: Gross up to $5.5k <br />Location: Whitley Road <br />Working Days: Shift Work (8am-8pm)  2 morning, 2 night, 2 off </p><p>Key Duties:</p><ul><li>Plan, execute and supervise all Facilities maintenance related work services.</li><li>Hands-on troubleshoot and repair M&E systems for smooth operations.</li><li>Manage Building / Facilities / M&E works and services for effective and efficient operations facilities performance.</li><li>Coordinate and supervise the M&E installation and maintenance work if needed.</li><li>Working closely with the client, sub-contractors, and the facilities team to resolve any technical issues. Attend M&E related meetings and involve in the preparation of related reports.</li><li>Assist in planning, controlling and coordinating of mechanical, electrical works.</li></ul><p>Requirements:</p><ul><li>Minimum Diploma or Degree in Engineering or Building / Real Estate/ Facilities Management or any related qualifications.</li><li>Facilities Maintenance operations background with at least 5 years of experience will be an added advantage.</li></ul><p>WhatsApp me at wa.me/6587801169 or press the APPLY NOW BUTTON.</p><p>By submitting your resume and/or personal information, you consent to the collection, use, and disclosure of your personal data by the company (or its designated agent) for the purposes of processing, administration and managing your job application.</p><p>Please be notified that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p>Sim Shu Hui Reg No.: R25129789<br />Griffin HR Consultancy Pte Ltd | EA License No.: 23C1449</p>",
